item.title: Can anyone help me with models?
item.dc:creator: @demonlover14 demonlover14
item.description:
@demonlover14 wrote:

Either try the search bar first. . .
But you prolly wouldn’t to to search for so I’ll tell you.
Ok this kinda a leech. . . but;
First thing is find a client that does have all he skills.(Also dugoneerin is just been released)
Then take out all the models from them, if needed.(Self expltory to know)
And the int’s outta class8.java.
And then NEALY put the ints in ur class8.java.
Then put ALL the models needed in your model folder;
Then last but not least log in, and type “add model (model id)” for all of them.(Inculding just the model numbers from them if any.)
Then restart clien and your good to go.
